{
  "stem": "1895.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that work on the ramp at Auschwitz [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was probably the closest that any onlooker has come to see the Holocaust in action without being directly involved in it, because I worked on a work unit which was charged with building something on the ramp.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were building a-- a hole in the ground, which later-- which we knew to be-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they later filled it with water.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was supposed to be a fire prevention thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I was able for these several months-- the key months in Auschwitz, I was able to be on the ramp and witness all of the deportations.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The thing that I talked to you about, Chaim Rumkowski who arrived at that particular time, I witnessed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I witnessed exactly and I remember the day very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When he arrived, there was a commotion on the ramp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saw these several SS officers came over to this white-haired Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they seemed to be giving him a lot of attention.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, we asked the others who that was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they told us that he is Chaim Rumkowski, who was at that point called the King of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, I saw them, the SS talking to him very amiably, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as they did, they walked with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as they talked, they walked towards the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the last I saw of him is they walked him right into the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that was the end of the Chaim Rumkowski.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I also saw many other things which are a little hard to describe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was one train I remember that came in that consisted of World War I Jewish veterans.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
